title: Bunbury (Carlos J. F.)
body: English botanist and paleontologist who studied the Madeiran flora and the fossil plants of the parish of S. Jorge in 1853. E. Remarks on the Botany of Madeira and Teneriffe (Journ. of the Proceed. of the Linn. Soc., 1856); and On Some Vegetable Remains from Madeira (Geological Journ., 1859).

1853: Madeiran flora and fossil plants of the parish of S. Jorge
